msgctxt "44_Ultimate Move: Tiger Puppetry"
msgid "Saejima can <Color:7>grab an enemy by the legs<Color:Default>\\r\n"
"and swing them around like a weapon.\\r\n"
"\\r\n"
"[Grabbing an Enemy's Legs]\\r\n"
"Press <Action:Battle_Drop_Weapon@Combat> near a fallen enemy's legs to grab them,\\r\n"
"then use <Action:Battle_Normal_Attack@Combat> or <Action:Battle_Heavy_Attack@Combat> to swing them around."
